messages.messageBody:
In a message dated 6/11/2003 5:07:17 PM Central Daylight Time,
Unschooling-dotcom@yahoogroups.com writes:
> INFJs are gentle, caring, complex and highly intuitive individuals.
> Artistic and creative, they live in a world of hidden meanings and
> possibilities. Only one percent of the population has an INFJ
> Personality Type, making it the most rare of all the types.

Funny....my dh is an INTJ and it said the SAME thing!! Said it was the rarest
and most misunderstood. I think I'm going to go read all of the types and see
what it says.

Ren
